{"tid":1685300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用最少成本贏最多","createTime":"2019-10-31T12:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T15:03:49.000Z","uid":212454,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"166417d20b6eeeab50e82bfa55dcb845254eff7b","tid":1685300,"uid":212454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"流程如下<br />\n<br />\n1 所有大日子都事先網上不停CALL馬, 例如今晚HALLOWEEN, XMAS, 12月31煙花, 要CALL到狗狗出聲話會預期有示威活動, 市民人身安全受威脅等等<br />\n<br />\n2 不停放風狗狗會用盡方法去封路, 去阻止活動進行<br />\n<br />\n3 我地仲要配合, 周圍叫人唔好出去, 令到消費減少, 令商界加入去屌啲狗, 將商業成本轉嫁俾班狗<br />\n<br />\n佢地冇得拆既, 佢地出聲明話係謠言唔會封路, 我地可以照出, 佢地反口封路又多啲人屌, 佢地真係封路就影響經濟, i.e. 聽日會有新聞話今年HALLOWEEN生意係百年一遇咁差, 商界會不停屌<br />\n<br />\n4. 不停同啲藍屍講係狗狗搞垮香港經濟, 藍屍最緊張就係經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6b55cc1e6b08d6aa32a6dd71fa6b3718fcec93","tid":1685300,"uid":212454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6646aa257dc329b2b9905ea7ca27056538150ea8","tid":1685300,"uid":212454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aec568dc8b865e76cfc1e748359d61746334b85","tid":1685300,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"（公投）11.2好似有活動撞左時間<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n入嚟討論下幫手投票順便推post上熱門比多啲人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbe8a7e27fa4c7a527afd9caccd287974919d5f","tid":1685300,"uid":252064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRRDeX9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRRDeX9.jpg&h=7df1d17a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":